These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different pets are kept: turtle, snake
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, pilot
2 different games are played: canasta, billiard
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, plum
1. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
3. the pilot is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet      | turtle  | snake   |
| Job   | pilot     | analyst   |
| Game         | billiard | canasta |
| Food     | pomegranate | plum    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, november
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, red
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, badminton
1. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes grey is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Birthday          | december     | november |
| Color   | red | grey  |
| Flower           | azalea         | marigold     |
| Sport     | handball   | badminton    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
House: cottage, wooden
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, western
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, january
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
3. the cottage house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| House    | wooden     | cottage |
| Movie-Genre         | western | spy    |
| Birthday         | december         | january        |
| Music-Genre   | ambient         | d&b    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
