2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre      | satire     | musical |
| Birthday          | july   | january  |
| Color         | mauve | brown     |
| Flower   | tulip  | dahlia         |

