.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, tennis
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
City: marseilles, hamburg
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport      | swimming | tennis       |
| Birthday           | march      | august     |
| City   | hamburg       | marseilles   |
| Music-Genre           | country          | classical |

