.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, quad-bike
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, documentary
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, singing
There 2 different types of food: orange, papaya
1. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Transport           | quad-bike | taxi    |
| Movie-Genre   | western       | documentary |
| Hobby           | card-games         | singing    |
| Food         | orange    | papaya   |

