1. the polish is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Birthday      | october    | july   |
| Nationality          | polish     | dutch |
| House           | cottage | tower     |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | backgammon     |

