.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill
House: cottage, art-deco
There 2 different types of food: kale, potato
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, writing
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the art-deco house is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Cigar           | montecristo | dunhill |
| House   | cottage    | art-deco      |
| Food           | kale      | potato          |
| Hobby         | writing | dancing       |

